  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: As a user I want to be notified when I am added to group chat or someone has added me to contacts (but did not send anything yet)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nI want to be notified in both cases. Some design should be done there, @denis-sharypin please assist :)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n1. When someone scanned my contact code - new chat is created on my device on Home tab, but I am not notified about it (no new badge is shown or any other notification received)\r\n\r\n2. When someone has added me to group chat - new chat is created on my device on Home tab, but I am not notified about it (no new badge is shown or any other notification received)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/38934556-c130892e-4324-11e8-94f8-9f678bf27ed0.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: develop\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS",
